# Pinned upstream OpenWrt release for the StartWRT image build.
#
# The release is fetched as the upstream tag tarball
# (https://github.com/openwrt/openwrt/archive/refs/tags/v$OPENWRT_VERSION.tar.gz,
# overridable via OPENWRT_TARBALL_URL) and verified against
# OPENWRT_TARBALL_SHA256 before extraction — the integrity pin. For human
# reference: tag v25.12.5 == upstream commit f0a60eee2fe051741c643ea6118718aae1ef17fb.
#
# To move to a new upstream release: update BOTH values (sha256 of the new
# tag's tarball), then re-run `make start-wrt-openwrt-setup` — if a patch in
# openwrt-patches/ no longer applies, refresh it per CONTRIBUTING.md
# "OpenWrt tree".
OPENWRT_VERSION=25.12.5
OPENWRT_TARBALL_SHA256=19462c4d0d52824b33ae52f60ee5e66528bf103691aabdb5e1e15cc8924067df
